      "writtenOn": "2018-12-13T22:32:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It\u0027s copied from ShouldErrLike below. I made semantics similar.\n\nIf the user calls:\nShouldContainErr(multiError)\n\nWhat would you expect to happen?\n\nIn my opinion this should probably be changed to ShouldHaveLength 0 so that it succeeds on nil MultiError and empty MultiError. Otherwise what\u0027s the alternative? Always succeed? Always fail? Neither make much sense to me.",
      "parentUuid": "588341c3_3d07f3a1",
