        "id": 1001907
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-12-13T22:38:01Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think this is mirroring the same functionality of `So(x, ShouldErrLike)`... which in retrospect is a bit questionable (I wrote this originally, and I don\u0027t think we\u0027ve actually used this form at all)",
      "parentUuid": "588341c3_3d07f3a1",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 34,
